text:
To start, there is to know that before to choose to study communication, I wanted to go in the commercial domain. But then, when I discovered in details the economy and what could be related to this, I totally changed my mind and at this moment I had the feeling that it wouldn't correspond to me. So I was lost and I decided to see a woman who were working in my highschool and who had as job to help students like me to clarify what could they do in the future, especially in their studies. I told her what was I enjoying to work on in my courses and It were about to observe, to see and to understand how the people acts in the society and in various situations. My wish were to learn all of the mecanism which could influence a person on its acting. According to all of this stuff, the woman told me that the Communication area correspond not bad to my profile and that globaly why I'm here today and I don't regret it yet and I hope that I wouldn't regret in the future. Also, later I would love to work in the social medias because the communication is clearly an important point on them so it's interresting.
 This webpage performs keylogging of input typed into a textbox. In other words, when focused on the textbox below, the page will record each time you hit a key or select text with your mouse. All of the data is stored locally on your machine in the DOM and is downloadable as a JSON file. More information about the motivation of this project and the format of the produced data are available gere.
